	<div class="postzoom"><h1><a href="2012_04_28_what_every_programmer_should_know_about_memory">What Every Programmer Should Know About Memory</a></h1>
<p>I was just thinking about this paper today: Ulrich Drepper's "What Every Programmer Should Know About Memory".</p>

<p><a href="http://www.akkadia.org/drepper/cpumemory.pdf">http://www.akkadia.org/drepper/cpumemory.pdf</a></p>

<p>If you haven't read it, and you are a programmer, then you really need to read this paper.</p>
